column2: SELECT #'#'# as objID, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj, p.type, p.ra, p.dec, f.mjd_u as mjd_u, f.mjd_g as mjd_g, f.mjd_r as mjd_r, f.mjd_i as mjd_i, f.mjd_z as mjd_z, p.u, p.g, p.r, p.i, p.z, p.Err_u, p.Err_g, p.Err_r, p.Err_i, p.Err_z, petroMag_u, petroMag_g, petroMag_r, petroMag_i, petroMag_z, petroMagErr_u, petroMagErr_g, petroMagErr_r, petroMagErr_i, petroMagErr_z FROM fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) n, PhotoPrimary p JOIN Field f ON p.fieldID = f.fieldID WHERE n.objID = p.objID
